{"tid":730670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【《體育世界》播埋本周】余詠珊落刀 解散體育組 30人炒剩5人","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T15:16:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9eb38beaff2fe1529b002fc7fb6452d350f6af","tid":730670,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"日前「蘋果」率先報道TVBI大裁員之後，無綫亦會大裁員，其中余詠珊嘅非戲劇科亦要裁。之前有傳聞指余詠珊向下屬稱係李寶安要佢炒100人，今日再有消息傳出，余詠珊決定向佢管嘅體育組開刀，解散體育組約30人，全組本來有30人，只炒剩5人，撥入新聞組，而體育組主管就被提早退休，《體育世界》最後一集於今周播出後正式完成歷史任務，MyTV Super體育台亦只做到8月15日。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》收到消息，無綫今日已通知員工，明天正式派信。<br />\n<br />\n本報晚上向無綫行政總裁李寶安求證，他承認體育組解散：「無綫電視在2014年播放世界盃期間，面對嚴重盗播情况，而近期亦留意到盗版侵權活動有增無減。無綫電視將來購買和播放昂貴體育賽事會更加謹慎，並會在中短期間集中播放及報道港澳地區的體育康樂活動。體育科將併入新聞及資訊部，而製作部節目包裝小組的工作性質亦會調整，整合後會減少二十多名人手。」<br />\n<br />\n問李寶安《體育世界》面臨停播，同埋MyTV Super體育台要cut，他稱：「We shall not run a streaming sport channel. Instead, we shall broadcast sport events on individual program basis. Also we shall focus more on HK and Macau sport events, like Macau Formula Racing, etc.」<br />\n<br />\n鍾志光回覆本報時，對於體育組地震、《體育世界》亦要停播，他大感愕然：「吓？我唔知喎！我同韓毓霞冇做《體育世界》好多年啦！我近年集中拍劇多啲，同埋做奧運、世界盃或者龍舟呢啲大型項目。唉！聽到呢個消息好突然，有家庭負擔嘅同事真係大鑊！我都要同啲同事了解吓先。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58405379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58405379&d=wfwEOzrquiZZpp7W%2FLLl%2FgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fcb2273a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58405379&h=c45a6ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58405379</a>"},{"pid":"14f84d583e366ded88b7e692b7c2b5e02bdf3dcc","tid":730670,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"呢個應該係好多人既童年夢想"},{"pid":"18b555796e04637a6938a30edf177f6c1bb2f6b9","tid":730670,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"球迷世界都一早冇咗⋯"},{"pid":"8dcf987658cc141733ab314d38eae65559fa2fbe","tid":730670,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"成個cctvb執左佢啦"},{"pid":"1f7630002eec315058af51a28d4a519aa0f7f1dc","tid":730670,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"正式痴左孖根"},{"pid":"ac1f660b8d49c9471f0ee5204767d8ab08178d27","tid":730670,"uid":144546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"由音樂已經入哂腦"},{"pid":"e787f0540cbaf2765cab2f274e5b1b3e82a9b216","tid":730670,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/230346_1f5c46130752d1f11688e9d1f02da7ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F230346_1f5c46130752d1f11688e9d1f02da7ea.png&h=46da5401&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0afc0e044298b0048fddb9fd3bb977a4e1513341","tid":730670,"uid":161935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"炒左邊d人？李思雅？余德丞？"},{"pid":"b006fec1bdf6551934553b68206e06a857536889","tid":730670,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a86eeef013f2c2d503781bf5161fff8f0f51b4da","tid":730670,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"睇肉世界"},{"pid":"b52527e5be86841b62e9e273d86de378e3156c63","tid":730670,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"難怪最近少左咁多打手開post, 叫cctvb 播世界盃"}]}